%% Data Flow Diagram - Text Generation Inference Server (TGIS)
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-2.6/text-generation-inference.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as gRPC Client
    participant Router as Router (Rust)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    participant Batcher as Dynamic Batcher<br/>(in Router)
    participant Shard0 as Model Shard 0 (Python)<br/>Unix Socket gRPC
    participant ShardN as Model Shard N (Python)<br/>Unix Socket gRPC
    participant GPU0 as GPU 0<br/>PCIe/NVLink
    participant GPUN as GPU N<br/>PCIe/NVLink

    Note over Client,GPUN: Flow 1: Unary Text Generation (Generate)

    Client->>Router: gRPC Generate Request<br/>fmaas.GenerationService/Generate<br/>Optional TLS + mTLS
    Router->>Router: Validate request<br/>(max_new_tokens, params)
    Router->>Batcher: Queue request for batching
    Batcher->>Shard0: Prefill (Unix Socket gRPC)<br/>generate.v1.TextGenerationService
    Shard0->>GPU0: CUDA inference
    GPU0-->>Shard0: Prefill result

    loop Token Generation
        Batcher->>Shard0: NextToken (Unix Socket gRPC)
        Shard0->>GPU0: CUDA inference
        GPU0-->>Shard0: Next token
        Shard0-->>Batcher: Token result
    end

    Batcher-->>Router: Complete generation
    Router-->>Client: gRPC GenerateResponse<br/>Optional TLS

    Note over Client,GPUN: Flow 2: Streaming Text Generation (GenerateStream)

    Client->>Router: gRPC GenerateStream Request<br/>fmaas.GenerationService/GenerateStream
    Router->>Batcher: Queue for batching

    loop Server-Side Streaming
        Batcher->>Shard0: NextToken (Unix Socket)
        Shard0->>GPU0: CUDA inference
        GPU0-->>Shard0: Token
        Shard0-->>Batcher: Token result
        Batcher-->>Router: Token
        Router-->>Client: gRPC Stream Token<br/>(server-stream)
    end

    Note over Client,GPUN: Flow 3: Tensor Parallel Multi-GPU

    Note over Shard0,ShardN: NCCL Collective Communication (TCP:29500)
    Shard0->>ShardN: NCCL AllReduce/AllGather<br/>TCP port 29500
    Shard0->>GPU0: CUDA compute (shard 0 partition)
    ShardN->>GPUN: CUDA compute (shard N partition)
    GPUN-->>ShardN: Partial result
    GPU0-->>Shard0: Partial result
    ShardN-->>Shard0: NCCL gather results

    Note over Client,GPUN: Health & Metrics

    Client->>Router: HTTP GET /health (3000/TCP)
    Router-->>Client: 200 OK
    Client->>Router: HTTP GET /metrics (3000/TCP)
    Router-->>Client: Prometheus metrics (tgi_*)
